controal statement's
match-case:
3.10 
--it is used check for multiple condition
syntax:
n=int(input('enter number'))
match n
	case 0:
		print("zero")
	case 1:
		print("one")
	case 2:
		print("two")
		===========================
day=int(input('enter number'))
match day
	case 0:
		print("sunday")
	case 1:
		print("mon")
	case 2:
		print("thues")		
