=============================
if-else:
syntax:

if condition:
	statement-1
else:
	statement-2
	
if,else keyword's
if the condition return true, then st-1 is excuted. and st-2 is not excuted
if the condition return fasle, then st-1 is not excuted. and st-2 is  excuted

